      "raw_text": "SEATTLE, Aug. 19,-According\nto a statement made here by A. H..\nHoagland, chief engineer of the\nGreat Northern, that line Will soon\ncommence double tracking on the\nwest slope of the Rocky mountains\nbetween Whitetish, Mont, and Sum-\nNIT. The greater part Of the old\nline will be rebuilt on this division.\nWork will be commenced as soon\nas the engineers have finished the\nplans."
    }
